                      <h5 class="card-title">Arthur Street estate</h5>
		      <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Status: </h6>
		      <p class="card-text"><p>In Sep 2019, the Mayor approved the demolition of 262 homes on Bexley’s Arthur Street estate - to be replaced by 320, all social rent being replaced by London Affordable Rent, at a net loss of 134 ‘social’ homes</p>
</p>
                      <a target="_blank" href="/estates/bexley/arthurstreet/" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Open in new tab">Read more here: <i class="icon-popup"></i></a>
