		    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Thamesmead South (phase 1)</h5>
		      <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Status: </h6>
		      <p class="card-text"><p>226 homes are currently in the process of demolition on Bexley’s Southmere site of the Thamesmead estate, to be replaced by 1,622 new homes of which only 39% affordable and replacement ‘social’ housing at up to 80% market rent.</p>
</p>
                      <a target="_blank" href="/estates/bexley/thamesmeadsouth/" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Open in new tab">Read more here: <i class="icon-popup"></i></a>
