		      <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Status: </h6>
		      <p class="card-text"><p>2,100 homes are earmarked for demolition on Ealing’s South Acton estate with replacement ‘social’ housing at up to 80% of market rent.</p>
